{"tid":277774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"檔主九龍城街市「守株待兔」　獨力捉偷生果賊","createTime":"2017-06-10T02:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T04:51:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"deec9c44e3ecde5b198608328c1b6d9199311460","tid":277774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170610/s00001/9bc720f6ee72e799bedfea3e8a413dde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F9bc720f6ee72e799bedfea3e8a413dde.jpg&h=aed35087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍城街市發生盜竊案。一名數日前遭賊人偷走生果的生果檔男檔主不甘損失，相信賊人食髓知味會再次犯案，獨自駕駛私家車泊在街市對面馬路，坐在車內「守株待兔」，其間果欄工人如常將水果送來，放在街市門外，至凌晨4時許，檔主目睹一名中年漢在街市門外徘徊，對方將一籮約值1300元糯米糍荔枝拖過馬路，檔主隨即下車制止及報警。警員接報到場，拘捕中年漢，正調查他是否與數日前偷生果案有關。<br />\n<br />\n32歲姓賴檔主表示，約兩周前將檔口搬入九龍城街市，果欄工人通常凌晨將水果送來，由於街市未開門，工人將水果放在街市門外，賴兩日前失去兩箱約值600多元的美國水蜜桃，因此部署捉賊。<br />\n<br />\n涉案男子姓黃，57歲，涉嫌「盜竊」罪名被捕。"},{"pid":"ec5c12993d203a68b347611b42978a1220dca6c1","tid":277774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497058345733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497058345733&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=85ee4972\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497058345733&h=48a0f3fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497058345733</a>"},{"pid":"0b25ac59938217df6a2ff0a7a588d481a877488f","tid":277774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68285b395097532246450088236fbf5a471b2124","tid":277774,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c903fa1c0c472ea6d01840aee9dc8ee40b0b06","tid":277774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170610/large/1497044267_aec2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170610%2Flarge%2F1497044267_aec2.jpg&h=9294fec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n偷水果賊被警方拘捕。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170610/large/1497044283_ff70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170610%2Flarge%2F1497044283_ff70.jpg&h=36217853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生果檔主賴先生協助調查。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170610/large/1497044298_585a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170610%2Flarge%2F1497044298_585a.jpg&h=bd1cf086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方起回被偷走一籮糯米糍荔枝。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170610/large/1497044329_f484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170610%2Flarge%2F1497044329_f484.jpg&h=81a08858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水果放在街市門外。(黃江奇攝)"},{"pid":"8c6b0933613c3367ba72750f49440898c7e9f41e","tid":277774,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6347ad48b749d91687958e916b98534a93c70e3c","tid":277774,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:32:01.000Z","msg"